                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14206780" author="hishamsaid" created="Tue, 11 Nov 2014 18:37:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sample PDF&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14206781" author="hishamsaid" created="Tue, 11 Nov 2014 18:37:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sample rendered pages&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14206824" author="tilman" created="Tue, 11 Nov 2014 18:59:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This one is not a &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2423&quot; title=&quot;Page tree handling needs rewriting&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2423&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2423&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; regression, I just tested with rev 1633472, and there is the same problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14206872" author="jahewson" created="Tue, 11 Nov 2014 19:22:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This file throws an exception on my working copy in which I&apos;m working on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2423&quot; title=&quot;Page tree handling needs rewriting&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2423&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2423&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, so it looks like I might be able to fix this at the same time.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14265747" author="jahewson" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 06:21:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The PDF is missing a number of ExtGState and XObjects.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14265748" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 06:22:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1649738 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jahewson&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jahewson&quot;&gt;jahewson&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1649738&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1649738&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2495&quot; title=&quot;Black shapes in the background of some rendered pages of some PDFs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2495&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2495&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: ExtGState = Extended Graphics State&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14265754" author="jahewson" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 06:37:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The black is caused by a giant glyph, possibly an italic letter &lt;tt&gt;I&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14265763" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 06:53:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1649739 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jahewson&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jahewson&quot;&gt;jahewson&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1649739&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1649739&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2495&quot; title=&quot;Black shapes in the background of some rendered pages of some PDFs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2495&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2495&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Check for FontMatrix in Top DICT before falling back to Font DICT&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14265766" author="jahewson" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 06:54:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This was due to the font having a FontMatrix value in one of its Font DICTs rather than in its Top DICT, which was confusing a fallback mechanism for invalid fonts.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14265824" author="tilman" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 08:16:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;While the issue PDF is now rendered very nicely, italic is lost in the file &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1094&quot; title=&quot;Pattern colorspace support&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-1094&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-1094&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-094730.pdf, page 4: The titles STRUCTURALLY HIGHER ROCKS and STRUCTURALLY LOWER ROCKS are no longer italic. Italic also lost on page 14, the latin sounding terms at the end of &quot;figure 6&quot;. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-679&quot; title=&quot;Corruption of Arabic output due to Japanese bug fix&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-679&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-679&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-toobig.pdf is also incorrect now, the glyphs are too bold.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14265974" author="lehmi" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 11:33:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;All fonts have at least a default font matrix value in its Top DICT after parsing. Therefore the new if clause added in &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1649739&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;r1649739&lt;/a&gt; is always false, so that the font matrix of the Top DICT is used in any case.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14266447" author="jahewson" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 17:30:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for spotting that - I&apos;ll have to move the repair code into the parser.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14266448" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 17:31:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1649882 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jahewson&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jahewson&quot;&gt;jahewson&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1649882&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1649882&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2495&quot; title=&quot;Black shapes in the background of some rendered pages of some PDFs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2495&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2495&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Perform CIDFont FontMatrix repair when parsing&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14266569" author="tilman" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 19:02:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Works fine now!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                    </comments>
